<span style="font-weight: bold;">Order Status</span><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;" id="a1">Q: What if I forget my Order Number?</span><br />A: Your order number is included in your Order Confirmation email with an automatic link to your Order Status on FiberStore.com. When you order by phone an associate will give you your order number. It is a good idea to save your Order Confirmation email or write down the number for future reference. If you forget or misplace your order number you can get it by contacting Customer Service Center via email at service@ecoptical.com  or by calling +86-75583003611 or Live Chat.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;" id="a2">Q: How will I know if FiberStore.com received my order?</span><br />A: Once an order you have placed for delivery has been processed, you will receive a confirmation via email. The confirmation will contain the expected delivery date, your shipping address, your order number and any other changes to your order.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;" id="a3">Q: How can I check the delivery status on my order?</span><br />A: To check the delivery status of your order, please log in and go your account and on the track a order page you can track your order conveniently or you can contact us directly for status.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;" id="a4">Q: How long do you keep my Order Status history?</span><br />A: The My Orders section is one of the great new features on FiberStore.com. Your Order Status history will go back 90 days and will reflect your orders that were placed on FiberStore.com.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">Shopping</span><br style="font-weight: bold;" /><br style="font-weight: bold;" /><span style="font-weight: bold;" id="b1">Q: What methods of payment does FiberStore.com accept?</span><br />A: We currently accept Paypal, Western Union and Bank Transfer. We ensure your Credit Card information is 100% safe and secure.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" id="b2">Q: Can I get a discount if I order large quantities of an item?</span><br />A: Buy in large quantities and you can save even more. Simply call +86-75583003611 or Live Chat or email to service@ecoptical.com  for a volume discount.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;" id="b3">Q: Can I add or delete items from my order if I change my mind?</span><br />A: Most orders are transmitted almost immediately to our warehouse where it is processed very quickly and shipped out. If you want to change your order, please let us know as soon as possible, by calling +86-75583003611 or Live Chat with us. We will check the status of your order and attempt to make the necessary changes. If your order has already been transmitted to our warehouse for shipping, we will not be able to make changes to the order and it will ship as is. If you cannot call or Live Chat with us, please send us an email and we will make the necessary adjustments as noted above.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" id="b4">Q: How will I know whether or not my order has been approved for credit and shipped?</span><br />A: When you place your order on the Internet, we will email and call you to confirm your order and then arrange shipment.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;" id="b5">Q: What do I do if I want to cancel my order?</span><br />A: Call us right away at +86-75583003611 or Live Chat with us or send us an email. Most orders are transmitted almost immediately to our warehouses and we may not be able to cancel your order, please let us know as soon as possible.<br /><br /><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;" id="b6">Q: What happens if there are issues with my order?</span><br />A: If there are any issues with your order, you will be contacted by a customer service representative.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" id="b7">Q: How do I get in touch with FiberStore.com if I have a problem with my order?</span><br />A: Please call us at +86-75583003611 or Live Chat with us or send us an email (service@ecoptical.com ) if you need assistance with your order.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Returns</span><br style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" /><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" id="c1">Q: How do I return something I've ordered via the Internet?</span><br />A: You can go to your account and open RMA request, we will assist you at once or call us at +86-75583003611 or Live Chat with us or send us an email (service@ecoptical.com ) for help.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Web Site</span><br style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" /><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" id="d1">Q: What do I do if I can't remember my password to get into the web site?</span><br />A: If you forget your password, you can click the button “forget password”, then type your username (email address), later you will received email from us of new password. Then you can use this new password to log in and update your password in personal file section.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">Miscellaneous</span><br style="font-weight: bold;" /><br style="font-weight: bold;" /><span style="font-weight: bold;" id="e1">Q: FiberStore price-match guarantee</span><br />A: FiberStore.com promises a price match guarantee. If you find a price lower than ours on the Qualified Internet Retailer sites listed below, and you meet the eligibility requirements listed below, we will match the price, or within 3 days of your FiberStore.com purchase and we will give you the difference.<br />When requesting a price match, please be aware that prices will be compared on the following criteria:<br />(1). Our Price Match Guarantee does not apply when you use coupons, rebates, promotional offers, free shipping, or product-bundle pricing on the order.<br />(2). Price comparisons include the product price plus shipping & handling charges when calculating the competitor's total price in comparison to www.FiberStore.com’s product price and lowest priced shipping method for that item.<br />(3). Our Price Match Guarantee does not apply to membership pricing.<br />(4). Our Price Match Guarantee is limited to up to three (3) of the same product, shipped to the same address.<br />(5). The Price Match Guarantee is subject to change at any time.<br />Qualified Internet Retailers:  eBay.com, Amazon.com, BestBuy.com, Compusa.com, Hardware.com, TigerDirect.com, PROVANTAGE.com<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;" id="e2">Q: Warranty---what is this?</span><br />A: If any product proves defective during this warranty period, FiberStore.com, at its option, either will repair the defective product without charge for parts and labor, or will provide a replacement in exchange for the defective product.<br />In order to obtain service under this warranty, customer must notify ECptical.com of the defect before the expiration of the warranty period and make suitable arrangements for the performance of service. Customer shall be responsible for packaging and shipping the defective product to FiberStore.com. Customer shall be responsible for paying all shipping charges, duties, taxes and any other charges for products returned to any other locations.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" id="e3">Q: Lead-time---what is this?</span><br />A:  Lead time is the period between a customer's order and delivery of the final product. A small order of a pre-existing item may only have a few hours lead time, but a larger order of custom-made parts may have a lead time of weeks, months or even longer. Ecotpical.com produces and stocks a full range of transceivers and other fiber optic products. Normally we can ship within 24 hours, but for some products the lead-time will be 2-3 days or longer. We will notify you of the lead-time over 3 days.<br /><br style="font-weight: bold;" /><span style="font-weight: bold;" id="e4">Q: Trusted by 5000+worldwide buyers---what is this?</span><br />A: We are so proud of our products trusted by 5000+worldwide buyers.<br />FiberStore R&D department with core technical knowledge provides strong innovative capability. FiberStore outstanding performance can meet the need of the customer special requirements<br />We strive to keep our operating expense as low as possible and negotiate for the best prices so we can keep your prices the lowest possible. <br />We are convinced that path to success is through excellence and customer service. Our customers are our number one priority. We know you have many choices of where to buy, so we do our best to provide the best products, at the best prices with the best possible support.<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" id="e5">Q: Money Back Guarantee---what is this?</span><br />A: 7 Day Money Back Guarantee<br />A Money Back Guarantee Makes for Virtually 100% Customer Satisfaction<br />We are convinced that path to success is through excellence and customer service. Our customers are our number one priority. We know you have many choices of where to buy, so we do our best to provide the best products, at the best prices with the best possible support.<br /> <br /><span style="font-weight: bold;" id="e6">Q: Phone number-why ask?</span><br />A: We ask for your phone number just incase we need to reach you for any reason regarding your order with FiberStore.com, and international order by FedEx or DHL and so on need your phone number. We do not rent, share, or sell your personal information, ever.<br /><br style="font-weight: bold;" /><span style="font-weight: bold;" id="e7">Q: Remember me login? ---What is this?</span><br />A: We provide this option to keep you from having to enter your user name and password every time you return. We’ve added this feature solely for your benefit, to save you time and to keep you from having to remember yet another password!<br /><span style="font-weight: bold;"><br /></span><!--End FAQlist dl.d--><!--End FAQlist dl.f-->

